<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">• قال الدَّارَقُطْنِيّ:</span> ضعيف. <span class="c2">«الضعفاء والمتروكون»</span> <span class="c2">(٦١٠)</span> ، و <span class="c2">«السنن»</span> ٤ ٢٣٠.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>• وقال ضعيف الحديث. <span class="c2">«السنن»</span> ٣ ٣٠.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>